            <h2>ðŸ“‹ Order of Operations</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Create Persons table</strong> first</li>
                <li><strong>Create Bank Accounts table</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Create Bank Accounts â†” Persons relation</strong> (One-to-One)</li>
            </ol>
            
            <hr>
            
            <h3>What's happening:</h3>
            <ul>
